Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.geoweb.web.workload.freq

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompositeValuedSet
    A set consisting of smaller finite continuous intervals, associated with normal distributions.
    ConstFreqFunction
    A function that returns a constant for every time instance.
    FiniteValuedInterval
    A finite interval of values with an associated normal distribution or a constant.
    FrequencyFunction
    We are representing the generated workload as a Poisson distribution over a function of time - Po(f(t)).
    PeriodicStochasticFrequencyFunction
    A frequency function that defines periodic behaviour - for example the workload repeats everyday/week etc.
